HEADWORD: oxidization
<hw>oxidization</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The process of oxidizing; the
addition of oxygen to a compound with a loss of electrons. The process
always occurs accompanied by reduction.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> oxidation, oxidisation.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

